{
  "texts": [
    "Generative AI (GenAI) lets designers create high-quality synthetic images using descriptive text prompts [24,55].",
    "Text-to-image AI applications like DALL•E 3 [51], stable diffusion [48] and midjourney [47] enable designers to generate novel images or iterate their visual design.",
    "GenAI also produces a wide range of creative output beyond images.",
    "In music composing, GenAI can produce consistent and high-quality music with text input [2].",
    "In 3D graphics creation, GenAI can produce 3D assets using solely text or 2D images without requiring 3D models [53]."
  ]
}